												<DIV>I don't want to super flame or rant this "Nerf" but I have a few questions that might make me feel this is a Justified nerf.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Q1) In game toons invited to the "meeting" (non soe or guide/gms) what levels were they, how long have they played the bard class.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Q2) How many of these peeps are Time/Elemental flagged, VP keyed, VT keyed, and GoD flagged? (thus possibly being uber in many opinions)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Q3) Play times of these people? (&lt;10hours a week, etc.)</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Q4) How often they solo vs. group vs. raid, this would be a big thing about their play time vs. XPing.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>These things I would like to know. I dont care for a new expansion I wont be able to go to for god knows how long, don't overly care for the opinions of those that only play for raids cause they are maxed out in AA's and got everything in game that us lower lvls want. I get to play maybe 15 hours a week. Taking AE kiting from me (and alot of other non-65 uber peeps) makes being a bard useless for the older servers. I for one like spending a couple hours a day AE kiting getting up to 30% in those hours, before loggin and hoping I get to do this again the next time I play. Being in the Navy and leaving for weeks at a time really cripples me in my gaming time. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>SoE made a nerf a while back that limits Solo xp (why i stop quading with my druid) but now either I chant kite or charm kite, which to me takes the same amount of time as AoE kiting seems pointless to remove AoE from a Bards life. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>There are problems people have mentioned in this post that havent been answered or even responsed to. Auto-circle removed from the game, forcing the "cheaters" (afk macro SoB's) to actually sit down and play, is a good point. This new zone in Omens effects what lvls, under 65? Not likely, I know SoE can make limits to the zone to effect bard AoEing in there. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I kite, lose xp, get up kite again and keep trying, HOPEFULLY I can end up ahead at the end. </DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>When I watch a class solo a mob that should be at least groupable it makes me mad that SoE would do this to us bards.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Anyway, over and done with. Prob wont make a difference in any way. I been playing and paying for 4 years and dont wanna see the game die out because of too many ubers and there nerfs.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>Raknia</DIV>
