												<DIV>Ya but you can walk into a dungeon, fight your way through it, find a named and kill it in toe to toe combat.&nbsp; That is an ability of your class.&nbsp; If SOE made some way for you to lose that ability it would be ridiculous.&nbsp; Bards don't go into dungeons of comparable lvl alone... unlike many many classes.</DIV>
